  <pb n="4" facs="11"/>
        <lg corresp="#AN4">
          <l><lb n="14"/>mullai vainnuṉai tōṉṟa villamoṭu,</l>
<l>paiṅkāṟ ko<lb n="15"/>ṉṟai meṉpiṇi yaviḻa,</l>
<l>virumpu tirittaṉṉa māyiru <gap reason="lost"/><lb n="16"/>piṟ<del>p</del></l>
<l>paralava laṭaiya viralai teṟippa,</l>
<l>malarnta ñālam <gap reason="lost"/><lb n="17"/>mpuṟak koṭuppak,</l>
<l>karuvi vāṉaṅ kataḻuṟai citaṟik,</l>
<l><gap reason="lost"/><lb n="18"/>cey taṉṟē, kaviṉpe<sic>ru</sic> kāṉaṅ,</l>
<l>kuraṅkuḷaip po<gap reason="lost"/><lb n="19"/>ta koycuvaṟ puravi,</l>
<l>narampār<add place="above">p</add> paṉṉa vāṅkuvaḷ pariya<gap reason="lost"/></l>
<l><lb n="20"/>pūtta poṅkart tuṇaiyoṭu vatinta,</l>
<l>tātuṇ paṟa<gap reason="lost"/><pb n="5" facs="12"/><lb n="1"/>pētuṟa lañci,</l>
<l>maṇinā yārtta māṇviṉait tēri</l>
<l>ṉu<lb n="2"/>tukkāṇ ṭōṉṟu<sic>ru</sic> kuṟumpoṟai nāṭaṉ</l>
<l>kaṟaṅki<lb n="3"/>cai viḻavi ṉuṟantaik kuṇātu</l>
<l>neṭumperuṅ kuṉṟat tama<lb n="4"/>ṉṟa kāntaṭ</l>
<l>pōtavi ḻalari ṉāṟu</l>
<l>māytoṭi yarivaini<lb n="5"/>ṉ māṇalam paṭarntē.</l>
        </lg>
 <p corresp="#AN4-kilavi">
<lb n="4"/>e-tu- tōḻi talaimakaḷaip paruvaṅkāṭṭi vaṟam puṟuttiyatu
